                    <li><strong>Authentication:</strong> Remember your login status</li>
                    <li><strong>Security:</strong> Protect against fraud and unauthorized access</li>
                    <li><strong>Form Data:</strong> Temporarily store form information during document generation</li>
                    <li><strong>Session Management:</strong> Maintain your session across pages</li>
                </ul>

                <h3>Performance and Analytics Cookies</h3>
                <p>These cookies help us understand how visitors use our website:</p>
                <ul>
